{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"My travels to Afghanistan"},{"time":3000,"text":"began many, many years ago"},{"time":6000,"text":"on the eastern border of my country,"},{"time":9000,"text":"my homeland, Poland."},{"time":12000,"text":"I was walking through the forests"},{"time":14000,"text":"of my grandmother's tales."},{"time":18000,"text":"A land where every field hides a grave,"},{"time":23000,"text":"where millions of people"},{"time":25000,"text":"have been deported or killed"},{"time":28000,"text":"in the 20th century."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31000,"text":"Behind the destruction,"},{"time":33000,"text":"I found a soul of places."},{"time":36000,"text":"I met humble people."},{"time":38000,"text":"I heard their prayer"},{"time":40000,"text":"and ate their bread."},{"time":42000,"text":"Then I have been walking East for 20 years --"},{"time":47000,"text":"from Eastern Europe to Central Asia --"},{"time":50000,"text":"through the Caucasus Mountains,"},{"time":52000,"text":"Middle East,"},{"time":54000,"text":"North Africa,"},{"time":56000,"text":"Russia."},{"time":58000,"text":"And I ever met more humble people."},{"time":62000,"text":"And I shared their bread and their prayer."},{"time":65000,"text":"This is why I went to Afghanistan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":68000,"text":"One day, I crossed the bridge"},{"time":72000,"text":"over the Oxus River."},{"time":74000,"text":"I was alone on foot."},{"time":76000,"text":"And the Afghan soldier was so surprised to see me"},{"time":78000,"text":"that he forgot to stamp my passport."},{"time":81000,"text":"But he gave me a cup of tea."},{"time":83000,"text":"And I understood"},{"time":85000,"text":"that his surprise was my protection."}]},{"cues":[{"time":88000,"text":"So I have been walking and traveling,"},{"time":91000,"text":"by horses, by yak, by truck, by hitchhiking,"},{"time":94000,"text":"from Iran's border"},{"time":96000,"text":"to the bottom, to the edge of the Wakhan Corridor."},{"time":101000,"text":"And in this way"},{"time":103000,"text":"I could find noor, the hidden light of Afghanistan."},{"time":110000,"text":"My only weapon"},{"time":112000,"text":"was my notebook and my Leica."},{"time":117000,"text":"I heard prayers of the Sufi --"},{"time":119000,"text":"humble Muslims,"},{"time":121000,"text":"hated by the Taliban."},{"time":123000,"text":"Hidden river,"},{"time":125000,"text":"interconnected with the mysticism"},{"time":127000,"text":"from Gibraltar to India."},{"time":130000,"text":"The mosque where the respectful foreigner"},{"time":135000,"text":"is showered with blessings"},{"time":137000,"text":"and with tears,"},{"time":140000,"text":"and welcomed as a gift."}]},{"cues":[{"time":144000,"text":"What do we know"},{"time":146000,"text":"about the country and the people"},{"time":148000,"text":"that we pretend to protect,"},{"time":151000,"text":"about the villages"},{"time":154000,"text":"where the only one medicine"},{"time":156000,"text":"to kill the pain and to stop the hunger"},{"time":158000,"text":"is opium?"},{"time":160000,"text":"These are opium-addicted people"},{"time":163000,"text":"on the roofs of Kabul"},{"time":166000,"text":"10 years after the beginning of our war."},{"time":170000,"text":"These are the nomad girls"},{"time":173000,"text":"who became prostitutes for Afghan businessmen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177000,"text":"What do we know about the women"},{"time":179000,"text":"10 years after the war?"},{"time":181000,"text":"Clothed in this nylon bag,"},{"time":183000,"text":"made in China,"},{"time":185000,"text":"with the name of burqa."},{"time":189000,"text":"I saw one day,"},{"time":191000,"text":"the largest school in Afghanistan,"},{"time":194000,"text":"a girls' school."},{"time":196000,"text":"13,000 girls"},{"time":199000,"text":"studying here"},{"time":203000,"text":"in the rooms underground,"},{"time":206000,"text":"full of scorpions."},{"time":209000,"text":"And their love [for studying]"},{"time":212000,"text":"was so big that I cried."}]},{"cues":[{"time":217000,"text":"What do we know"},{"time":219000,"text":"about the death threats by the Taliban"},{"time":222000,"text":"nailed on the doors"},{"time":224000,"text":"of the people who dare to send their daughters to school as in Balkh?"},{"time":230000,"text":"The region is not secure, but full of the Taliban,"},{"time":233000,"text":"and they did it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235000,"text":"My aim is to give a voice"},{"time":237000,"text":"to the silent people,"},{"time":240000,"text":"to show the hidden lights"},{"time":244000,"text":"behind the curtain of the great game,"},{"time":247000,"text":"the small worlds ignored by the media"},{"time":250000,"text":"and the prophets of a global conflict."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252000,"text":"Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":254000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}